# Task: Analyze GitHub Repository 'becoming_church'

## Checklist
- [x] Visit https://github.com/sungcheolkim78/becoming_church
- [x] Analyze core content (README, files, folders)
- [x] Identify theological themes, church vision, and specific data
- [x] Evaluate feasibility for building a "program" or "app"
- [x] Report back with summary and analysis

## Findings
- **Repository Name**: `becoming_church` (교회가 되다)
- **Core Content**: 40-day Bible study/morning prayer materials.
- **Source**: Pastor Lee Kang-woo (Good Tree Church).
- **Structure**:
    - `yaml_40days`: Structured source data (Day, Title, Song, Prayer, Verses).
    - `md_40days`: Generated Markdown files containing full Bible text.
    - Scripts: `gen_40days.py`, `gen_mpage.py` (uses `py_kbible` for automation).
- **Theological Content**: Focuses on "Becoming Church" (the nature and growth of the church community).
- **Feasibility**: 
    - **High**: The data is already structured in YAML, which is ideal for apps (mobile/web).
    - **Automation**: Existing scripts demonstrate easy content generation.
    - **AI Integration**: Perfect for an AI agent to deliver daily lessons, generate media (Shorts), or facilitate spiritual growth programs.
